short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Make every YouTube video into a Blue-Archive Sechi Cameo!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A chrome extension that makes every thumbnail on youtube have Blue Archive art from the artist BlueSechi!(Now with Firefox compatibility and toggle!)

I got this idea from MrBeastify and Jambofy:
Jambofy: https://github.com/LiamHarrison25/Jambofy-Extension
Mrbeastify: https://github.com/MagicJinn/MrBeastify-Youtube

GitHub page for this extension:
https://github.com/IsaacSohn/Sechify

Support me on kofi if you want and can: https://ko-fi.com/chikenuwu

If you wanna help increase the image count, you can send any cutouts to me at chikenuwu0415@gmail.com or my discord @chikenuwu. Keep in mind that the dimensions are 1280x720
